1) Login to machine using the local administrator
2) Open settings
3) Choose Network and Internet
4) Change adapter options
5) Choose ethernet internet 0
6) Choose Properties
7) Highlight Internet Protocol 4
8) Choose Properties
9) Choose "use the following dns server" and use 192.168.1.21
10) Open sysdm.cpl
11) Click change
12) Choose Domain 
13) Type windomain.local
14) Use admin creds
15) Should be domain joined!
